  "about": {
    "label": "About Us",
    "title": "Built by Makers, for Makers.",
    "subtitle": "3DZAAP Print Manager is not just another tool — it's the mission to professionalize 3D printing worldwide.",
    "story_p1": "3DZAAP was created from scratch, thinking about the real challenges we face every day in the world of digital fabrication. We know that running a 3D printing business goes far beyond operating a machine — it is controlling invisible costs, anticipating stockouts, professionalizing customer service, and above all, turning hours of work into real profit.",
    "story_p2": "Our platform was born from the frustration of disorganized spreadsheets, quotes made 'by head', and filaments running out at the worst moment. We decided to create the solution we always wanted to have: a complete, intuitive, and accessible system that puts the maker in full control of their business.",
    "val1_title": "Precision",
    "val1_desc": "Every calculation matters. Our cost engine considers energy, wear, material, and risk — so you never charge below fair value again.",
    "val2_title": "Transparency",
    "val2_desc": "No hidden fees, no fine print. Your data is yours, and our platform is open about what it charges and what it offers.",
    "val3_title": "Innovation",
    "val3_desc": "We constantly evolve with community feedback. Every feature is designed to solve real production problems."
  },
